==English==

===Etymology===
From {{bor|en|fr|effigie}}, from {{der|en|la|effigiēs||likeness, effigy}}, from {{m|la|effingō||represent, portray}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|en|/ˈɛfədʒi/}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[dummy]] or other [[crude]] [[representation]] of a [[person]], [[group]] or [[object]] that is hated.
# A [[likeness]] of a person.

